  • Perception of Foreign Accent
    This project focused on native English speakers perception of L2 speech errors. L2 errors were ranked according to their perceptual accentedness. A Naive Discrimination Model (NDL) was build to approximate accentedness. Preliminary results were published here. A web application was developed to implement the NDL method.
